text: Mihai Şulţ (born 7 March 1933) is a Romanian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman featherweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Romania Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Timișoara
title: Mihai Şulţ
